. Etymology. The name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lowry &amp; Berents" authorityYear="1996" box="[1726,1907,358,396]" class="Malacostraca" family="Ischyroceridae" genus="Notopoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="10" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
